                    <li>Providing information and data on all services inside and outside Kuwait and issuing specialized journals related to the Company's purposes.</li>
                    <li>Conducting studies and collecting data in the service field of all sectors in the country, analyzing them for creating databases, and establishing and managing data centers to facilitate access to such data, through initiating subscriptions to individuals and companies, in cooperation and coordination with the concerned authorities.</li>
