                    <li>Providing administrative and technical workers for all local public and private companies.</li>
                    <li>Recruitment of specialized technical workers.</li>
                    <li>Manage employment contracts with companies, governmental and non-governmental bodies and employment of specialized and general workers.</li>
                </ul>
